<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[الصَّديق]</span>: المصادق،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَوْ صَدِيقِكُمْ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
